    "body" : "<p>CharSequence is an interface and String is its one of the implementations other than StringBuilder, StringBuffer and many other.</p>\n\n<p>So, just as you use <code>InterfaceName i = new ItsImplementation()</code>, you can use <code>CharSequence cs = new String(\"string\")</code> or simply <code>CharSequence cs = \"string\";</code></p>\n"
